	(text_box "Solder jumper JA1 is used when Unit-A is not loaded, solder jumper JB1 is used when Unit-B is not loaded, solder jumper JC1 is used when Unit-C is not loaded, and solder jumper JD1 is used when Unit-D is not loaded.\nUnit-A is loaded first, then Unit-B, then Unit-C, and then Unit-D."
